            . I am in the East India Company's service. The prisoner was employed in the warehouse in <placeName id="t18211205-74-crimeloc458">Cutler-street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18211205-74-crimeloc458" type="placeName" value="Cutler-street"></interp>
